content.title: Onboard Stargaze (stargaze-1) onto Quicksilver
content.description:
Summary

Stargaze is a decentralized, community-owned app chain for NFTs.
The Quicksilver development team proposes onboarding the Stargaze Zone onto Quicksilver to unlock liquidity for $STARS stakers. This action will enable the deposit of $STARS (ustars) and the minting of $qSTARS (uqstars).

Timing

The onboarding of the Stargaze Zone will be effective when the proposal passes at the end of the voting period.

Voting Outcomes

 * If you vote YES on this proposal, you approve onboarding Stargaze Zone
 * If you vote NO on this proposal, you do not approve onboarding Stargaze Zone
